The performance panel controls the playback, stopping, pausing, and recording of a single score and/or any active algorithms using a set of tape-transport-like buttons.  Tempo can be adjusted at any time via a slider.  A MIDI Sytem Real Time "Start" command is sent to all NoteFilters and Instruments.\
